As we have studied about the abstract class and the final class
the sealed class is combo of both
How ? -> Look Here -> Abstract class are meant to be inherited and final class cannot be inherited.
SO there should be some class which can be allowed to inherit by some classes while not allowed to be extend it.

Those classes permitted to inherit are required to be sealed, non-sealed or final and must extending the sealed class.

if subclass is made sealed it is also required to give permission to next classes to extend it so will be using non sealed.
final subclass are also not allowed to be extended again by any other class

it is used in design of application.


Class ke jaise interface me hota hai sealed kaa lekin iss barr final keyword nhi de sakte interface ko